        <abstract> 
<p>Carus will soon begin translating 5th ed. of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p>  
<p>Sale of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> is satisfying.</p> 
            <p>C. J. Dub will write popular work on CD’s theory.</p> 
<p>Gustav Jäger has written on it [<hi rend="italic">Die Darwin’sche Theorie und ihre Stellung zu Moral und Religion</hi> (1869)].</p> 
        </abstract>
